{"tid":736910,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［訴苦］有無人男朋友成日講變態鹽濕野","createTime":"2018-07-10T14:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T01:25:03.000Z","uid":35639,"like":1264,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"9bea282a5048a61b732ee9cb06b34e6a5d6731b1","tid":736910,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"我男朋友無論係私人地方定公眾場合都好鍾意同我講變態野<br />\n側邊無咩人都算<br />\n有時行緊街身邊勁多人佢都要講 仲要都幾大聲<br />\n今日終於因為咁嘈左場大交<br />\n<br />\n話說放左工一齊食飯<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢見到我食緊腸仔就話：我好想放條賓周入你個口<br />\n搭枱個女仔已經投以一個鄙視既目光<br />\n<br />\n我：大庭廣眾你唔好講呢d野啦<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要唔知錯笑住咁講:咁我真係好想放條賓周入你個口嘛<br />\n<br />\n我終於爆發:想就要即刻講出黎？你識唔識控制自己呀？我夠想啦，我會唔會咁多人係隔離都要講呀？<br />\n<br />\n之後飯都無食曬頭也不回走左<br />\n佢打左十幾次電話我都無聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我知你睇緊個post架，你反省完先搵番我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"a48a4271f37e8b339d3587a15c7c31c8902b836c","tid":736910,"uid":100347,"like":523,"dislike":14,"score":509,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:54:40.000Z","msg":"有冇糖濕"},{"pid":"727eefdc1989b9e678fc86578368b9181918c498","tid":736910,"uid":38461,"like":434,"dislike":3,"score":431,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:54:50.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"0f1fd66f8b62e70fd0b93bcc968d51bccc4ba7ef","tid":736910,"uid":8762,"like":278,"dislike":4,"score":274,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"咁撚柒on9 你都唔飛佢，係真愛"},{"pid":"ef491589a916facf7d18e7dadc5bd21e735df9d4","tid":736910,"uid":29080,"like":683,"dislike":3,"score":680,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"咁我真係好想放條賓周入你個口嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5589a3f2945b2a82e6885ad3a9f03d82912a16e","tid":736910,"uid":194012,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:55:29.000