10,"uid":9863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"睇到句我夠想啦 笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fba44979b0f01553c2c0caed663567f6cf964cb","tid":736910,"uid":180980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:38:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2af86b02a243446da7932615dc2654d555889c75","tid":736910,"uid":167118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"fb33242116dbec6274a4923ad1b5883d965c70fb","tid":736910,"uid":165202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"我都好中意講但會識分場合<br />\n你男朋友...幼稚囉係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ebb5867368375248120bfdeb81e9aba3bc1be0","tid":736910,"uid":82312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bea282a5048a61b732ee9cb06b34e6a5d6731b1","tid":736910,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"我男朋友無論係私人地方定公眾場合都好鍾意同我講變態野<br />\n側邊無咩人都算<br />\n有時行緊街身邊勁多人佢都要講 仲要都幾大聲<br />\n今日終於因為咁嘈左場大交<br />\n<br />\n話說放左工一齊食飯<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢見到我食緊腸仔就話：我好想放條賓周入你個口<br />\n搭枱個女仔已經投以一個鄙視既目光<br />\n<br />\n我：大庭廣眾你唔好講呢d野啦<br />\n<br />\n佢仲要唔知錯笑住咁講:咁我真係好想放條賓周入你個口嘛<br />\n<br />\n我終於爆發:想就要即刻講出黎？你識唔識控制自己呀？我夠想啦，我會唔會咁多人係隔離都要講呀？<br />\n<br />\n之後飯都無食曬頭也不回走左<br />\n佢打左十幾次電話我都無聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我知你睇緊個post架，你反省完先搵番我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗公格"},{"pid":"9c2201f4802f548961dfd7cdcb9b94a7e8063a67","tid":736910,"uid":111372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"我係成日講，但你男朋友病程仲勁過我好似<br />\n係D靜既餐廳講呢D野盡量唔俾人聽到啦"}]}